name: Seasons of Love
description:
The artwork story :
Season’s love changes in time, from silly and blind,
Into something beautiful, steady and fine.
And she’s learned it’s moves, it’s changes, it’s rhymes,
Now she is happy, in a true love sublime.

digital painting 2480 x 2670 px
